genome mapped.

00:40.200 --> 00:42.200
Constantine, my old friend.

00:42.200 --> 00:43.700
-You showed.
-Of course.

00:43.700 --> 00:46.266
I have been at Mundia-Tel
my entire career.

00:46.266 --> 00:49.133
What people thought was
bedrock was really bullshit.

00:49.133 --> 00:51.133
