finally see the truth.

00:51.133 --> 00:53.400
Why aren't you  prosecuting
the investment banks

00:53.400 --> 00:55.300
and hedge funds
for insider trading?

00:55.300 --> 00:57.333
[amplified voice] Go ask
the 81 convicted felons

00:57.333 --> 00:59.400
of financial crimes
currently serving time.

00:59.400 --> 01:02.200
Don't go all
Charles Foster Kane on me.

01:02.200 --> 01:05.133
-You know I've never seen it.
-You have to immediately,

01:05.133 --> 01:07.700
projected on a big screen
on film.

01:07.700 --> 01:09.467
The Statue of Liberty
attempted bombing case

01:09.467 --> 01:10.667
needs to come off
your plate.

01:10.667 --> 01:13.133
-I'm sorry?
-Eastern needs that case.

01:13.133 --> 01:16.033
I've been doing this
for two years around the clock.

01:16.033 --> 01:18.567
[Bobby] So I came up here to
unplug and I, you know, can't.

01:18.567 --> 01:20.533
How do you do it, man?

01:20.533 --> 01:22.734
Hmm. I play, man.

01:22.734 --> 01:25.433
-Sell everything.
-Everything?

01:25.433 --> 01:28.166
Take it slow,
control the bleeding.

01:28.166 --> 01:31.066
Then we'll dump sector by sector
starting with telecom.

01:31.066 --> 01:33.233
-People will think --
-That I'm out.

